## ⏱️ Response Times

- Social media messages: typically within **24–48 hours**.
- Bug reports via GitHub Issues: acknowledged as soon as possible; critical issues prioritized.

---

## ❓ Frequently Asked Questions

**My views aren't counting — what should I do?**
Views update in near real time. If your dashboard looks stale, refresh the page first. If the issue persists, message us with a screenshot of your Earnings Dashboard.

**How do payouts work?**
You earn ₦200 per 1,000 views. Once you pass the 1,000-view minimum payout threshold, your balance becomes eligible for payout. Contact support with your account email to initiate a payout.

**I posted a job but can't see it.**
New job listings may take a moment to appear. If it's still missing after an hour, reach out with your listing title.

**I found a bug.**
Please [open an issue](../../issues) with steps to reproduce, your device/browser, and a screenshot if possible.

---

## 🔒 Reporting Abuse or Content Concerns

To report inappropriate content, impersonation, or abuse, message us on [Facebook](https://facebook.com/southerngist) or [X](https://x.com/southernreporto) with a link to the content. All reports are reviewed.

